hopobject.body: Could I have a statement, please? erythromycin 250 mg ec cap Built to house images of the British great and good, the NPG has had to move with the times. And getting this exhibition by arguably the greatest pop figure of the age (the first in a British museum) within its once hallowed walls represents a massive piece of cultural product placement. Dylan benefits (he isn’t after all a professional artist); and the gallery benefits from the large numbers of first-time visitors who will be drawn to its portals.
